<para style="p">

  <verse number="25" style="v" />Brothers, pray also for us.</para>

<para style="p">

  <verse number="26" style="v" />Greet all the brothers with a holy kiss.

  <verse number="27" style="v" />I request of you by the Lord that this letter be read to all the brothers.</para>

<para style="p">

  <verse number="28" style="v" />May the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you.</para>